        <h1>Multicloud communication for Kubernetes</h1>

        <p>Skupper is a layer 7 service interconnect.  It enables
          secure communication across Kubernetes clusters with no VPNs
          or special firewall rules.</p>

        <p>With Skupper, your application can span multiple cloud
          providers, data centers, and regions.</p>
